FAIL_TO_PASS: when program sent SIGUSR2 then executableSubcommand sent signal too
when program sent SIGTERM then executableSubcommand sent signal too
when execArgv --inspect=9240 then spawn execArgs using port 9241
when command has exitOverride and executable subcommand fails then program exit code is subcommand exit code
when execArgv --inspect then spawn execArgs using port 9230
when program sent SIGINT then executableSubcommand sent signal too
when execArgv empty then spawn execArgs empty
when program sent SIGHUP then executableSubcommand sent signal too
when program sent SIGUSR1 then executableSubcommand sent signal too
